Kennecott Utah smelter back on stream . Kennecott Utah Copper Corp ' s smelter is back on stream and will reach full capacity later in the year , company spokesman Louie Cononelos said . " The smelter has started , " Cononelos said . " Everything is ramping up as planned . " The smelter began operating Tuesday . The 310 , 000 short tons per year smelter was shut April 15 for 42 days of maintenance to iron out glitches which have plagued the new plant since its commissioning . " We plan to be at full capacity later in the year , " Cononelos said . ( ( Huw Jones , New York Commodity Desk 212 - 859 - 1646 ) ) 
